Place your welding PDF documents in this folder.

Accepted format : PDF (.pdf)
Examples        :
  - AWS_D1.1_Structural_Welding_Code.pdf
  - Welding_Handbook_Vol1.pdf
  - MIG_Welding_Reference_Guide.pdf

After adding PDFs either:
  A) Use the Gradio UI  →  Documents tab  →  Upload PDFs  →  Build Index
  B) Locally: python -c "from retriever import Retriever; Retriever()"
